text: Fred Talbot (born 1949) is a British former teacher and television presenter. Fred or Fredrick Talbot(t) may also refer to: *Fred Talbot (baseball) (1941–2013), Major League Baseball player *Frederick Talbot, rugby league footballer of the 1930s for Wales, Huddersfield, and Keighley *Fred Talbott, U.S. congressman *Frederick Hilborn Talbot, Permanent Representative of Guyana to the United Nations
title: Fred Talbot (disambiguation)
